      "rationale": "NIH is directly computed as the primary QoI. Shear stress and residence time are tracked as secondary QoIs. Linkage to clinical hemolysis threshold is documented. Achieved level 3 due to incomplete uncertainty attribution for residence time distribution."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
