      "rationale": "The validation activity is a numerical simulation of the same geometry at the same operating conditions. While geometrically and kinematically representative, it is not an experimental activity and does not independently validate the blood damage model against physical measurements. Relevance to COU is geometrically high but methodologically insufficient. Achieved level 2."
